DESCRIPTION: An enhanced watchlist for Wikimedia projects.
LASTREVONLY: Show only the latest change per page
FLAGS: Show flags instead of language names
LOGEVENT_DELETE_REVISION: <user> changed visibility of a revision on page <page>
LOGEVENT_PROTECT_MODIFY: <user> modified protection on page <page> with parameters {{protection_level}}
LOGEVENT_PROTECT_MOVE: <user> moved protection settings from <page> to <page title={{target_title}}>
LOGEVENT_BLOCK_BLOCK: <user> blocked <user name={{title}}> with an expiry time of {{duration}} with parameters {{flags|list}}
LOGEVENT_BLOCK_REBLOCK: <user> changed block settings for <user name={{title}}> with an expiry time of {{duration}} with parameters {{flags|list}}
LOGEVENT_RIGHTS_RIGHTS: <user> changed group membership for <user name={{title}}> from {{oldgroups|list}} to {{newgroups|list}}
LOGEVENT_NEWUSERS_CREATE2: User account <user name={{title}}> was created by <user>
LOGEVENT_NEWUSERS_BYEMAIL: User account <user name={{title}}> was created by <user> and password was sent by email
LOGEVENT_RENAMEUSER: <user> renamed user <user name={{olduser}}> ({{edits}} edits) to <user name={{newuser}}>
LOGEVENT_TRANSLATION_ASSOCIATE: <user> added translatable page <page> to aggregate group {{aggregategroup}}
LOGEVENT_TRANSLATION_DISSOCIATE: <user> removed translatable page <page> from aggregate group {{aggregategroup}}
OAUTH_FAILURE_CONTENT: Authentication failed, you might have revoked the authorization for this application. Please logout and sign in again. Error information: {{error}}
SERVER_ERROR_CONTENT: No watchlist could be retrieved. This is an internal server error, please open a bug report if the problem persists.
API_ERROR_CONTENT: An API request failed with error code {{errorcode}} and error information: {{errorinfo}}
HIDEOWNEDITS: Hide my edits from the watchlist
EDIT: Edit this page in new tab
UNDO: Revert this edit, opens new tab with preview
ORES_OPTION: Show diffs for ORES predicted reverts
ORES_TOOLTIP: Automatically show diff for predicted reverts, see [[:meta:ORES]] for details.
FLAGGEDREVS_OPTION: Show diff for pending changes needing review
FLAGGEDREVS_TOOLTIP: Show diff for unreviewed changes, if you have the review permission for a wiki which uses the FlaggedRevs extension.
